name: Samsung Galaxy S20
description: The Samsung Galaxy S20 features a stunning display, powerful camera system, and fast performance. With its sleek design and cutting-edge features, it's a top choice for smartphone enthusiasts.

name: Apple Watch Series 6
description: The Apple Watch Series 6 is a powerful wearable device that tracks your health, keeps you connected, and helps you stay organized. With its advanced features and stylish design, it's the ultimate smartwatch for tech-savvy users.

name: Dell XPS 15
description: The Dell XPS 15 is a high-performance laptop with a stunning display, powerful processor, and sleek design. Whether you're a professional or a student, this laptop is perfect for multitasking, gaming, and productivity.

name: iPad Pro
description: The iPad Pro is a versatile tablet that combines the power of a computer with the portability of a tablet. With its stunning display, powerful processor, and support for the Apple Pencil and Smart Keyboard, it's perfect for work, creativity, and entertainment.
